  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL8">
<l>veṟuppoṭu camaṇar muṇṭar vitiyilcāk kiyarkaḷ niṉpāṟ</l>
<l>poṟuppari yaṉakaḷ pēciṟ pōvatē nōya tāki</l>
<l>kuṟippeṉak kaṭaiyu mākiṟ kūṭumēl talaiyai yāṅkē</l>
<l>aṟuppatē karumaṅ kaṇṭā yaraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the Jains, Śaivas, or the unfortunate Buddhists</l>
<l>speak hard-to-bear things about You with hatred,</l>
<l>one ought to depart, with that [listening] being a disease!</l>
<l>If I obtain the target, if it is possible [for me],</l>
<l>It is [my] duty to cut off [their] heads in that very place!</l>
<l rend="indent">Look, O You who are in the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
